#compdef opsecret
# Completion for Core's `opsecret` (zsh/op.zsh): a 1Password secret reference of the
# form <vault>/<item>/<field> (read as op://<that>). The value lives in 1Password, not
# on disk, and a live `op item list` would block completion on network + auth — against
# Core's non-blocking rule — so we DESCRIBE the argument rather than fetch it.
_arguments '1:vault/item/field reference:'
